106
00:16:15,140 --> 00:16:16,500
I, Mu Yun,

107
00:16:16,660 --> 00:16:17,860
greet Your Highness.

108
00:16:54,540 --> 00:16:55,400
Your Highness.

109
00:16:55,580 --> 00:16:57,640
