00:26:46,580 --> 00:26:47,660
They will be...

204
00:26:59,900 --> 00:27:01,900
If he can't persuade His Majesty...

205
00:27:26,900 --> 00:27:28,090
Prepare my zither

206
00:27:32,060 --> 00:27:32,930
