207
00:27:35,940 --> 00:27:37,020
Your Highness.

208
00:30:52,260 --> 00:30:57,340
[Hanyuan Palace]

209
00:35:29,300 --> 00:35:30,140
Because of me,

210
00:35:31,500 --> 00:35:33,420
